des: "An easy paleo-friendly dish that will have your mouth watering! Enjoy over pasta or brown rice or eat alone if you follow the paleo diet!"
ins: Melt coconut oil in a skillet over medium heat. Stir squash, tomato, walnuts, and garlic into coconut oil; cook and stir until heated through, 3 to 5 minutes.
